<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss money</title><updated>2025-05-18T04:49:21.421566+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>f93dbe923f26db31ae4d7d72bc6eac1e</id><title>星期一一開市日本人香港人人踩人賣金， 特朗普又出說由美國指定關稅</title><updated>2025-05-17T23:26:47+08:00</updated><author><name>bigwindwa</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T23:26:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572449587"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572449587"&gt;星期一一開市日本人香港人人踩人賣金， 特朗普又出說由美國指定關稅&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930444&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1522165947682966d2503ea7_97349307"/><published>2025-05-17T23:26:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>03a1188e48f07511b81fee64af109d72</id><title>綱上大陸不少人講。大陸肺炎在大陸再爆發</title><updated>2025-05-18T00:13:04+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T00:13:04+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572450204"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572450204"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16232510" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572450204" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250518/20250518_4935b3381152805c6b35VIfwLoLsqzrZ.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1e8d2b/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250518/20250518_4935b3381152805c6b35VIfwLoLsqzrZ.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16232510_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16232510&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2024_1200_x_675_px_78_.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (304.9 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-18 00:13&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 edwin8888 於 2025-5-18 00:23 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930494&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1522165947682966d2503ea7_97349307"/><published>2025-05-18T00:13:04+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1d3835accdc73f1a46776e79e1e81e9b</id><title>美國佬買入600公噸黃金</title><updated>2025-05-18T02:55:30+08:00</updated><author><name>cowisstarting</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T02:55:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572451246"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572451246"&gt;《MarketWatch》報導，根據世界黃金協會最新數據，美國在 2025 年前兩個月悄然自倫敦與瑞士進口逾 600 公噸黃金，約為美國最大金庫所在地諾克斯堡 (Fort Knox) 官方儲金的 13%。此舉引發市場關注，是否意味著美國正提前應對全球金融系統潛在的重置風險。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;儘管主流金融機構將此解釋為「避稅或貿易關稅前的囤貨行為」，但包括資深投資人與對沖基金分析師在內的觀察人士普遍認為，實體黃金大量移動至美國境內，背後可能有更深層的貨幣與地緣政治考量。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 cowisstarting 於 2025-5-18 12:40 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930543&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1522165947682966d2503ea7_97349307"/><published>2025-05-18T02:55:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5fc3d5d5b0c3ed3e57e1eea9cbff03c8</id><title>內地人炒港股美股開始收稅</title><updated>2025-05-18T04:17:49+08:00</updated><author><name>簡約樸素的石榴</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T04:17:49+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572451444"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572451444"&gt;已經好多內地人，準備放棄在香港證券行同銀行買賣股票、將資金轉去冇CRS嘅美國證券行、&lt;br&gt;可能當初考慮加入CRS,嘅官員都冇諗到會有咁嘅一日、其實我見到網上都冇咩人討論、實際上係一個好大嘅影響&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930552&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1522165947682966d2503ea7_97349307"/><published>2025-05-18T04:17:49+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ba40efa2a07b461b5aa4816512da3c71</id><title>所謂中國功夫只係馬騮戲。真打下。給泰臣一拳就搞掂了</title><updated>2025-05-18T07:00:27+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T07:00:27+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572451865"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572451865"&gt;番&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/v/18yqkSMbX4/" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.facebook.com/share/v/18yqkSMbX4/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930571&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1522165947682966